==Foghlam==
'S e aon de na bailtean as cudthromaiche ri taobh [[foghlam]] a tha ann am Pretoria.
Tha mòran oilthighean ann:
* ''University of Pretoria'', an t-oilthigh as motha na dùthcha,
* ''Tshwane University of Technology'', oilthigh teicneòlas
* ''University of South Africa'', ainm goirid: UNISA,  an t-oilthigh as motha a tha a’ dèanamh foghlam aig astar.
